"{\"uid\": \"newseu.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-10-Olympic-superfan-can-t-get-enough-of-the-Games-1vXjAx7WwIo-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  There are Olympic fans.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then there are 'superfans.'\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vivianne Robinson is a 'superfan.'\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 285, \"end\": 293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9734742522784372, \"rank\": 0.014798944351622566, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has attended seven Games, going all the way back to Los Angeles in 1984.\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 367, \"end\": 378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999842902981, \"rank\": 1.3947636342454894e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My mom was a volunteer,\\\" says Robinson.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9734742522784372, \"rank\": 0.014798944351622566, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She would take the press to meet the athletes, and would provide translations.\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She would bring me all the pins, which are mementos, from the athletes.\\\"\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The American is getting a lot of attention from her fellow fans in Paris.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 588, \"end\": 596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999947033035582, \"rank\": 2.0911402992017797e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 651, \"end\": 656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992346602, \"rank\": 7.654343306326527e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some want to trade pins, others want that all-important selfie.\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love the Games because of the atmosphere that you feel.\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You meet people from all over the world,\\\" she adds.\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Doing whatever it takes  But Robinson's Olympic journey has not always been smooth.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9734742522784372, \"rank\": 0.014798944351622566, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had to skip the 2008 Beijing Games after running out of money.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, she is doing whatever it takes to fund her obsession.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I worked two jobs to be able to come to these Olympics,\\\" says Robinson.\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9734742522784372, \"rank\": 0.014798944351622566, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I made necklaces in the morning in Venice Beach, and at night I bagged groceries.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1157, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venice,_Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999752494663, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Venice Beach\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venice,_Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venice,_Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It took me a long time to save up, and I worked very hard.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I probably spent $10,000!\\\"\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 'superfan' was on track to watch the Tokyo Games, but then the Covid-19 pandemic hit.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had about 30 tickets for those Games, and then they said, 'No spectators.\\\"\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I have been waiting eight years for this Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1513, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Fanning' the Olympic flame  Robinson has had nearly 40 tickets to events in Paris.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9734742522784372, \"rank\": 0.014798944351622566, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992346602, \"rank\": 7.654343306326527e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has watched athletes competing in a range of sports, but one event was extra special.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have already been to football, archery, badminton and tennis,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the best experience so far was watching Simone Biles in the gymnastics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Los Angeles, her home city, will host the next Games in 2028.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1847, \"end\": 1858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999842902981, \"rank\": 1.3947636342454894e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a sense, Robinson's journey will come full circle.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9734742522784372, \"rank\": 0.014798944351622566, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She may have to work a little more to watch the action in LA.\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's a price she's willing to pay.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everybody seems to be in a good mood at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I meet athletes and I see all these amazing cities,\\\" says Robinson.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2178, \"end\": 2186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9734742522784372, \"rank\": 0.014798944351622566, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never spent so much in my life as I did in Paris.\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2234, \"end\": 2239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992346602, \"rank\": 7.654343306326527e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's well worth it, and I would do it again.\\\"\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": 